When a task touches any of these domains, load the corresponding `.agents/skills/<name>/SKILL.md` instead of guessing API details:

| Domain | Skill to load | Key classes/APIs |
|--------|--------------|------------------|
| App setup, init, destroy, resize | `pixijs-application` | `Application`, `app.init()`, `app.stage`, `app.canvas`, `app.destroy()`, `ResizePlugin`, `CullerPlugin` |
| Render pipeline, WebGL/WebGPU | `pixijs-core-concepts` | `autoDetectRenderer`, `WebGLRenderer`, `WebGPURenderer`, systems & pipes |
| New project scaffolding | `pixijs-create` | `create-pixi` CLI, bundler-vite template |
| Scene graph fundamentals | `pixijs-scene-core-concepts` | Container vs leaf, transforms, render order, masking, `RenderLayer`, culling |
| Container operations | `pixijs-scene-container` | `addChild`, `removeChild`, `zIndex`, `sortableChildren`, `toGlobal`/`toLocal`, `destroy`, constructor options |
| Sprites, animation, tiling | `pixijs-scene-sprite` | `Sprite`, `AnimatedSprite`, `NineSliceSprite`, `TilingSprite` |
| Vector drawing | `pixijs-scene-graphics` | `Graphics`, `GraphicsContext`, `fill()`/`stroke()`, `FillGradient` |
| Text rendering | `pixijs-scene-text` | `Text`, `BitmapText`, `HTMLText`, `SplitText`, `TextStyle` |
| Custom geometry meshes | `pixijs-scene-mesh` | `Mesh`, `MeshSimple`, `MeshPlane`, `MeshRope`, `PerspectiveMesh` |
| Particle systems | `pixijs-scene-particle-container` | `ParticleContainer`, `Particle`, `dynamicProperties` |
| HTML overlays on canvas | `pixijs-scene-dom-container` | `DOMContainer`, `pixi.js/dom` |
| Animated GIFs | `pixijs-scene-gif` | `GifSprite`, `GifSource`, `pixi.js/gif` |
| Asset loading & caching | `pixijs-assets` | `Assets.load`, `Assets.init`, bundles, manifests, spritesheets, `parser` field, `unload` |
| Color manipulation | `pixijs-color` | `Color` class, hex/rgb/hsl, `tint`, `premultiply` |
| Events & interaction | `pixijs-events` | `eventMode`, `FederatedPointerEvent`, `hitArea`, `cursor`, drag, `globalpointermove` |
| Math & geometry | `pixijs-math` | `Point`, `Matrix`, `Rectangle`, `Circle`, `Polygon`, `toGlobal`/`toLocal` |
| Ticker & render loop | `pixijs-ticker` | `Ticker.add`, `deltaTime`/`deltaMS`, `UPDATE_PRIORITY`, `maxFPS`, `onRender` |
| Blend modes | `pixijs-blend-modes` | `add`, `multiply`, `screen`, `overlay`, `pixi.js/advanced-blend-modes` |
| Filters & effects | `pixijs-filters` | `BlurFilter`, `ColorMatrixFilter`, `DisplacementFilter`, `NoiseFilter`, `Filter.from()` |
| Custom shaders & batchers | `pixijs-custom-rendering` | `Shader.from`, `GlProgram`/`GpuProgram`, `UniformGroup`, custom `Filter` |
| Performance optimization | `pixijs-performance` | `GCSystem`, `cacheAsTexture`, object pooling, culling, batching, `PrepareSystem` |
| Accessibility | `pixijs-accessibility` | `AccessibilitySystem`, `accessibleTitle`, `tabIndex` |

**Fallback:** When no skill covers the API surface, WebFetch `https://pixijs.download/release/docs/llms.txt` for the canonical auto-generated docs index.

